Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之跟我们走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嘛  走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你很久了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长的命令拒绝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  进去吧  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有时会发出很可疑的骚动  还会听到奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…  我也不会感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管夏目你怎么否认  我始终相信你有种特别的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你并不喜欢  但我觉得那是很了不起的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该更自信一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  说来西村和北本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管那些不相信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实像是会有妖怪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有意思  我也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  {\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}笹{\r}田同学  我们去对面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就去看那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫多轨的小姑娘  还挺机灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  我们赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方确实不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么  真的有什么在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  在对方没发现我们之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂  你去哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话多轨她们也有危险  我去叫她们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音  小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  说不定那不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就打开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的上勾拳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎么会被关在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从气味来看  似乎不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在玩捉迷藏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是不小心盖子掉下来  就出不来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听到有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么  你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在这里  猫咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…兴趣真差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石尾海？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三班那个  就是被怪人追的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说可能是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是因为父母回家都很晚  他才变得说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被人欺负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  不知怎么的他朋友很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYEBYE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我关进箱子里的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说不是我了  我是来给你送东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙在追着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看  他还带着只超丑的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚远点！豆芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜板！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朴树！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妖！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  轻轻松松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  海你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定不会应付小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（豆芽）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（菜板）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（朴树）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（人妖）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比跟妖怪对峙受到的伤害还大…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真够烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  这个忘记给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  名牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  老师  你帮我带给那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！居然想用区区200日元就打发我这高贵的妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要纸的！纸钞！给我福泽谕吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（福泽谕吉：万元钞）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖怪追着…那孩子也能看见妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见妖怪的孩子…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也不像被人欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了他  那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是破坏了约定  就吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说的小鬼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多轨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你是第一次见到田沼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是五班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话等一下再说  赶快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家里有书上写了  说这附近会吸引妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你流血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候…  是刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血的味道会引来妖怪  快走吧  你也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖辈是阴阳师？所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是很凶暴的妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能对妖怪心软
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它们与人不同  是邪恶的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫海的孩子  真的能看到妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  不过如果能看到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保护他？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到不能坐视不管  就会马上出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  或许是我太傲慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  只觉得是自己在找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之前  还全都怪在妖怪头上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（你掉的东西）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉…掉的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  会给你的  回去给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪  猫咪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的兴趣真差劲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在我后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你吗  不是你在追我  把我关进箱子里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…之前的  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…说你是豆芽  菜板  人妖什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  啊  不…没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见  我道过歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个追着你的家伙  告诉警察比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  跟他们说了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道过歉了  你就别管我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别耍这种无聊的脾气！等到事情严重了就太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起  我这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没断  过几天就不会痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该如何把我的担心传达给他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对妖怪反而交往得更轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚好看到了  你的手受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想会不会是为了救我  被追着我的家伙攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次就由我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才跟过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里人还没回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说要保护我  这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下  你把我当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是我的保镖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准忘！也不好笑！真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  小妖怪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追着我来了的话  它的目标就不是海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它盯上海了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是它说过要吃掉小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小孩子的妖怪有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你想太多了  区区小妖怪的戏言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说小妖怪  我刚才还被它弄伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？在我不知道的时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一点小伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子！虽然你被吃掉我就能得到友人帐是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但让那种小妖怪弄伤我的东西  我心情是很微妙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常微妙！你懂不懂夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这微妙的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果海看不到妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上海的不是妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁把海关进棺材里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真可爱  是在等人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  保护那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以来  我每天放学后都和海一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多轨教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个箱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你不愿意就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早些时候  我就觉得被谁盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来发现电线杆后面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始以为只是变态  就没太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这应该在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  我被那家伙追赶  跑进了那栋房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是想躲进那个箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就出不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子被锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我记得没有锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨看不见  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这么说  夏目也看得见那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨  这里有妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着海往这边逃  你别追过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…  糟糕  被引过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海  快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我放它走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉的话你会很烦  而且我是个美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它的妖气吸走了不少  应该不会再来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨面无血色地跑来找我  过来一看就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要到什么时候才会长记性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多轨…是吗  老师  谢谢你  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摸鼻子！很痒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目能驯服妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是驯服  是它救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目！海！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多轨！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多亏了老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了够了够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海能看见妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么追赶他的是刚才那个妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像还没结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他把海关进棺材里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名  名取先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这次特意不想把你卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你自己牵扯过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  把海关进棺材里的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是关进去  而是封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要接近那孩子比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  到底是怎么回事  名取先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:51.02,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}人与妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海竟然是妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了消灭他才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干了什么！海做了什么要被人消灭的事吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你也该下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说重要的  到底是人  还是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

